					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12381176#post-4338530</guid>
				<title>Love it</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12381176/scp-3902#post-4338530</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2019 18:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>peppermint_legos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5515758</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So quickly after the new object class bars come out, a writer has already added a witty take-off on the situation, managed to meld dado into it, and come out with this awesome product.</p> <p>Is it a jumping-off story about the new format option? A lighthearted jab at all the extra info it adds? A conspiracy to popularize the new format? Who knows. It's delightful and clever and that's what matters to me.</p> <p>Minor thought: dado's letter to djkaktus is a little too&#8230;coherent for me. I'm used to dado using much more broken English &#8212; the word substitutions were good, but the grammar was&#8230;also <strong>too</strong> good.</p> <p>&quot;i need more franch to franchise&quot; was a riot, though</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
